WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:06.293
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for joining me today. Truly, I'm so glad you're here.

00:00:06.294 --> 00:00:15.439
You know, yesterday was a wow. I will forever be changed by what happened yesterday.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:22.957
And I know a lot of people, because they weren't seeing it and I was trying to describe what I was seeing, don't get it a lot.

00:00:22.958 --> 00:00:33.914
And the comment section kind of goes along with that. But today, I'm going to make it clear for you to let you understand what the Lord was showing me.

00:00:33.915 --> 00:00:44.768
We were just singing 'The Lord is here'like you saw, and all of a sudden I saw the Lord said, 'I'm here, Brandon.'And I heard Him so clear and I said, 'Oh, the Lord is here.

00:00:44.769 --> 00:00:49.431
The Lord is here. The presence of the Lord is filling my house.'And it was the glory.

00:00:49.432 --> 00:00:56.291
I could feel the glory. Diana was sitting on the other side of the camera yesterday. Braden was doing the editing, remember?

00:00:56.292 --> 00:01:06.246
She fell out and she was laying right here in the middle of the floor, and she was weeping before the Lord, but she started smelling the fragrance of the Father like she always does.

00:01:06.247 --> 00:01:17.839
When the presence of the Lord fills the room, Diana will smell this fragrance of the Lord and it smells like sweet honeysuckle and all these other things that she describes, and it's absolutely glorious.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:27.039
But I've never really smelled it, only glimpses. It will come and it fades away, and I can smell it, but it's never like it is for her.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:40.639
But all of a sudden, when I was telling you I was hearing somebody singing, people said, 'Oh, Brandon, you heard me singing.'No, I wasn't hearing something in the natural; I was hearing in the spirit.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:56.319
And all of a sudden, I heard them singing the song that I was singing: 'From glory to glory, He's changing us, changing us.'But it was multiple voices, and I froze.

00:01:56.320 --> 00:02:07.366
That's why I was—it freaked me out a little bit because I thought, 'Well, my goodness, Diana, you're singing, too.'But you know, she was laying down there, but it sounded like it was right here, right here, everywhere.

00:02:07.367 --> 00:02:21.957
And all of us: 'From glory to glory, He's changing us.'But I noticed one of the voices, and everybody goes, 'Who is Sister Lucy?'Her name is Lucy Harriott, I believe, is her name.

00:02:21.958 --> 00:02:33.243
She is a lady that used to pray as a prayer warrior. And she is the twin sister of Lynn Hammond, who has a church up in Minneapolis, Minnesota.

00:02:33.244 --> 00:02:38.875
And it's called Living Word Church. Living Word, I believe, is the church's name.

00:02:38.876 --> 00:02:42.698
And they have a great congregation. They're a spirit-filled church.

00:02:42.699 --> 00:02:50.434
They love the Lord and are really on fire. They're prayer warriors. They're a great prayer church. Her husband is Mimmon.

00:02:50.435 --> 00:02:54.177
And if you're not familiar with it, I'd encourage you to look them up.

00:02:54.178 --> 00:03:01.039
They're great people. So, I was hearing her when she used to be alive.

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:09.360
I heard old tapes and old CDs and things from back in the day. And I remember her voice, and I went, 'Diana, that's Lucy.

00:03:09.361 --> 00:03:18.799
I hear Lucy.'And Diana knew who it was because we love to listen to her old stuff from when she was alive. She passed away, I believe it was 2010.

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:25.598
Well, I could hear the voice of Lucy and I was like, 'What in the world is that?'because I knew it was her voice.

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:33.525
And all of a sudden, I saw like this circle before my eye right here, right here.

00:03:33.526 --> 00:03:41.114
It went poof and it popped out. It looked like a tunnel that was in the spirit realm right before my face.

00:03:41.115 --> 00:03:48.098
And I could see the edges of this tunnel that looked like clouds, almost like you would see cotton candy.

00:03:48.099 --> 00:03:57.235
That's a good way to describe it. Like cotton candy—pink, purple cotton candy, fluffy, cloud-looking cotton candy.

00:03:57.236 --> 00:04:03.836
And it was on the walls of this tunnel. And as it went up, it had ridges.

00:04:03.837 --> 00:04:13.128
But as I kept looking through it, the tunnel started moving and my spiritual eyes were moving with it, and I could see.

00:04:13.129 --> 00:04:18.613
And all of a sudden, I went through the tunnel up to where it ended, and there was a light there.

00:04:18.614 --> 00:04:22.326
Everything was lit up. I'm going to tell you that there was no darkness at all.

00:04:22.327 --> 00:04:47.439
But the light became brighter, and I looked through the tunnel, and then I could hear them singing even louder: 'From glory to glory.'And I asked the Father, 'What is this?'He said, 'This is the great cloud of witnesses.'All of a sudden, I could see everything within probably a 20-foot radius.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:58.372
I could see this massive tree, a beautiful oak tree with beautiful leaves on it that had no darkness on them or shadows at all.

00:04:58.373 --> 00:05:03.728
The leaves were all different kinds of shades of green, but there was no darkness.

00:05:03.729 --> 00:05:11.384
Like, you know, when you see leaves on top of each other, there are shadows on there, but there were no shadows on this tree.

00:05:11.385 --> 00:05:17.920
And the wood was beautiful, vibrant wood on this tree trunk, okay?

00:05:17.921 --> 00:05:26.499
I saw green grass all around. That was the first thing I saw because the tree was the tallest. As I'm coming up through this, I could see the tree.

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:38.603
But then I looked down, and as I'm coming up through this hole, this thing, whatever this was, this portal, I could see Lucy sitting in a rocking chair.

00:05:38.604 --> 00:05:48.308
And she had her head down like this, and she was rocking and she was praying. She was praying in this rocking chair.

00:05:48.309 --> 00:05:59.673
And then on the right side of her, right here, was Brother Halverson, who is another amazing prayer warrior in his time on the earth.

00:05:59.674 --> 00:06:04.396
He's no longer here either. And he was sitting next to her right here.

00:06:04.397 --> 00:06:11.293
And Brother Halverson was praying and he was saying, 'Minnesota, Minnesota.'And he was praying out Minnesota.

00:06:11.294 --> 00:06:19.839
And they were praying together about Minnesota. And I could hear them praying about Minnesota, and I'll get to that more in a minute.

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:27.279
Jeanie Wilkerson, who is another major prayer warrior, was sitting next to Brother Halverson.

00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:38.478
On this side was Rachel Teafatiller, who is another amazing prayer warrior in the time back in the 1950s, 1940s.

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:44.783
She was a prayer warrior at Collinsville where I go to church, and she went home to be with the Lord.

00:06:44.784 --> 00:06:48.699
She's praying next to Jeanie Wilkerson, who was friends with Kenneth E.

00:06:48.700 --> 00:06:58.913
Hagin and she prayed in the camp meetings and all kinds of stuff. She was a great prayer warrior, but they were so young.

00:06:58.914 --> 00:07:05.777
This was Jeanie Wilkerson, Rachel Teafatiller, and then Sister Woodworth-Etter.

00:07:05.778 --> 00:07:18.959
Sister, I know I probably butchered the lady's name, but Sister Woodworth-Etter was sitting next to Rachel Teafatiller.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:30.884
How I knew because I said, 'Lord, who is this lady with the double bun?'She had her hair up, big poofy Pentecostal hair, and it was a bun on top of a bun.

00:07:30.885 --> 00:07:41.939
And I thought, 'You never see that.'But she was wearing her hair as a bun on top of a bun, and she was very old-school Pentecostal looking—old-school.

00:07:41.940 --> 00:07:51.365
And I asked the Lord after—this is how I know. I was praying after it was over, after our prayer session, I said, 'Lord, what did you just show me?

00:07:51.366 --> 00:07:56.392
What was that?'He said, 'That's Sister Woodworth-Etter, Brandon. She's an elder.

00:07:56.393 --> 00:08:01.598
Go look her up.'So, I went and I had Diana—I said, 'Diana, would you look this name up?

00:08:01.599 --> 00:08:13.300
This is who the Lord said that other woman was, sitting next to Rachel Teafatiller.'And she looked, she goes, 'Oh my gosh.'Then there was another lady there, and I don't know who that was.

00:08:13.301 --> 00:08:24.689
I still don't. She was sitting, looking at Lucy, and I said, 'Lord, what are they doing? What are they doing?'after I could see all this stuff.

00:08:24.690 --> 00:08:32.956
But I don't say a lot of things that I'm saying, but I'm saying it in my spirit toward the Father, and you don't know I'm saying it because I'm talking to Him.

00:08:32.957 --> 00:08:42.626
And I said to Him, 'What are they doing?'He said to me, 'Brandon, this is a prayer group.'I'm like, 'A prayer group in heaven?

00:08:42.627 --> 00:08:54.177
Why are they praying?'He said, 'Brandon, they're praying on an assignment for the revival that's about to take place on the earth.'He said, 'They're assisting you.

00:08:54.178 --> 00:09:15.219
They're helping you.'I know the Bible says that Jesus is at the right hand making intercession for all of us, but I was like taken back by it because I was thinking, 'Is this biblical?'you know, because I don't know this in the Word, because I'm always questioning everything.

00:09:15.220 --> 00:09:26.208
But I know that as on earth, as it is in heaven, and that's the scripture that I'm going to go by, that they were praying in heaven and they're praying on the earth.

00:09:26.209 --> 00:09:36.077
And these people were praying. Were they crying? No. So I said, "Lord, what are they praying about?"And they were interceding for revival in Minnesota.

00:09:36.078 --> 00:09:49.971
I heard Brother Halverson kept praying for revival. And all of a sudden, Living Word Lynne Hammond's church—with Lucy as the head of the prayer group—she was sitting in a rocking chair.

00:09:49.972 --> 00:09:54.230
Now, I got to go back to this. What were the others sitting on?

00:09:54.231 --> 00:10:07.219
They were sitting on a patchwork quilt on top of the beautiful green grass. And each little square was purple and pastel colors.

00:10:07.220 --> 00:10:12.431
Beautiful pastel colors like Easter colors, beautiful Easter-like pastel spring colors.

00:10:12.432 --> 00:10:23.337
There was purple, blue, pink, and white, but it was all like these little squares. And there was a patchwork quilt.

00:10:23.338 --> 00:10:36.533
And on top of the purple squares, I could see beautiful little daisies with little white flowers with a yellow ring, a yellow little print on the inside of it.

00:10:36.534 --> 00:10:41.068
And they were all little bitty flowers on top of the beautiful purple squares.

00:10:41.069 --> 00:10:52.851
And on the blue squares were different things, but all the different flowers created a beautiful quilt that they were sitting on, praying.

00:10:52.852 --> 00:11:01.198
But at the corners of each of the squares where they joined together was a beautiful ribbon of yellow.

00:11:01.199 --> 00:11:09.740
A beautiful ribbon of yellow was at the corner of each four corners of all of the quilt pattern.

00:11:09.741 --> 00:11:22.914
It was like it ran up through, and I could see it, and at the edges was a beautiful embroidery of some kind of beautiful print that was around it, and it was so beautiful.

00:11:22.915 --> 00:11:30.628
But Lucy was sitting in a wooden rocking chair. It looked oak, and it was like an old one you would get at Cracker Barrel.

00:11:30.629 --> 00:11:39.385
You know, like if you're in America, we have a restaurant called Cracker Barrel, and they sell a wooden rocking chair that you sit on your porch with.

00:11:39.386 --> 00:11:46.423
And that's the kind of Southern rocking chair that it was. It's a real Southern thing.

00:11:46.424 --> 00:11:52.775
Wooden rocking chairs like this are what we have down in the South, and they sell them at Cracker Barrel and you can get them.

00:11:52.776 --> 00:11:57.253
That's the kind of wooden rocking chair Lucy was in. But she was at the edge of it.

00:11:57.254 --> 00:12:03.366
She wasn't leaning back in her chair; she was at the edge leaning forward, and Brother Halverson was leaning forward.

00:12:03.367 --> 00:12:15.919
And I could see Jeanie Wilkerson was leaning back, and the others, and they were all just interceding and praying for a revival in Minnesota.

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:24.039
As they were praying, I could hear them saying Minnesota, praying for Lynne Hammond's church, which is Living Word, which I told you.

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:27.533
And that's Lucy, her sister. But they were praying for this, right?

00:12:27.534 --> 00:12:42.765
And all of a sudden—I'm trying not to skip around—all of a sudden, I saw a massive fire break out inside of a Holy Ghost and fire—a wave of His glory hit that church.

00:12:42.766 --> 00:13:21.679
And the Lord spoke to me, and He said, "I visited this church in the '90s, Brandon."He said, "But this was with Lynne and her husband."And He said, "Brandon, I'm going to visit it with this new generation, and there will be a great move of My presence one more time on this church, and I will pour out My spirit, and there will be a mighty revival in Living Word as they were interceding for it."And I saw it like echo all throughout Minnesota, and people were getting born again by the tens of thousands.

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:37.034
The glory is coming, folks. But He was showing me hot spots. And as it became on fire, it became like a brush fire; it started spreading out.

00:13:37.034 --> 00:13:41.962
It didn't stay there on that church; it started spreading out.

00:13:41.963 --> 00:13:50.776
And there was charred ground on the land like you see when the fires are moving. And every one of the—I call them hot spots.

00:13:50.777 --> 00:13:57.590
There was a hot spot when I was praying; I saw it in Branson and Tulsa and Fort Worth.

00:13:57.591 --> 00:14:08.078
But then I looked to the east, and I saw hot spots popping up all over the east, Kentucky, Tennessee, all over the place.

00:14:08.079 --> 00:14:23.696
And He said, "The bluer the state..."Many said, "What are you talking about, the bluer the state?"He said, "The bluer the state, Brandon, which is Democrat, it's liberals."He said, "The bluer the state, the greater the harvest."That's what He said.

00:14:23.697 --> 00:14:28.120
"The bluer the state, son, the more liberal it is, the greater the harvest.

00:14:28.121 --> 00:14:35.967
Don't look at it as this dark blue, because the darker blue it is, the greater the harvest."That's what the Father said.

00:14:35.968 --> 00:14:46.647
Because Minnesota is very blue, very liberal, and the Lord said, "The greater the blue, the greater the harvest."Hallelujah!

00:14:46.648 --> 00:14:55.994
I tell you, I saw it. And then I looked to the west, and there were those hot spots popping up all over the place.

00:14:55.995 --> 00:15:02.432
They were all in Oregon, they were all in Washington, they were all in California, they were in Nevada, and they were popping up.

00:15:02.433 --> 00:15:07.119
And this is what He told me. You remember when I told you about the popcorn?

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:09.972
He said, "You don't know where the next revival is going to start.

00:15:09.973 --> 00:15:20.185
If you go heat up a pan, son, with some coconut oil in it, and you watch the pan, you don't know which one's going to pop next."He said, "That's the way this next revival is going to be.

00:15:20.186 --> 00:15:33.809
They're going to be popping all over the place."He goes, "Because you're not going to control it."A lot of people, when you have an Asbury or whatever, or a Brownsville or whatever, people try to control it after a while.

00:15:33.810 --> 00:15:38.792
"Well, you know, this is the way we should do it,"and they try to limit God in how He's doing things.

00:15:38.793 --> 00:15:43.268
"Well, you know, it's getting out of hand. People are getting too radical; they're getting too noisy.

00:15:43.269 --> 00:15:51.926
So, we've got to kind of corral this."And the Lord said, "You're not going to corral what's about to happen with your Pharisee thinking.

00:15:51.927 --> 00:16:05.322
God is going to have His way."And I saw, as they were praying, their prayers—when we were praying together as a family—their prayers were rolling out of heaven, and they were popping me in the stomach.

00:16:05.323 --> 00:16:15.091
And I was groaning the prayer, and we were assisting each other in prayer for the nations, for revival around the world.

00:16:15.092 --> 00:16:21.302
And He said, "Brandon, you'll notice they won't get tired because they're not in their earthly body anymore.

00:16:21.303 --> 00:16:25.194
They're in their glorified body, so they can pray all the time.

00:16:25.195 --> 00:16:27.626
They don't go, 'I've got to take a break. We've got to have nighttime.

00:16:27.627 --> 00:16:32.073
We've got to go eat.'They were praying like there's no time.

00:16:32.074 --> 00:16:35.995
There's no time in heaven, do you understand? So, they're continually praying.

00:16:35.996 --> 00:16:46.619
They lose track of time because they're in the glory, and they were interceding for us to have revival, praying for us to have a glorious outpouring.

00:16:46.620 --> 00:16:52.701
And I'm telling you, they were assisting. And as they were praying, the glory was coming out of them, and it was coming on me.

00:16:52.702 --> 00:17:00.375
And that's what we were feeling in my house, and I could feel it bubbling up out of my spirit.

00:17:00.376 --> 00:17:10.318
I was underneath that presence all night long. I felt it; it was so strong, like a cloak.

00:17:10.319 --> 00:17:14.841
And the Lord kept showing me a cloak coming on me. I could see it.

00:17:14.842 --> 00:17:40.615
And I told Diana, I said, "Boy, it's increasing."He said, "Heaven and earth are about to collide with the greatest harvest of souls and the greatest demonstrations and manifestations of My glory that this world has ever seen before."In a 24-hour period, Brandon, we're at the point of no return.

00:17:40.616 --> 00:17:48.091
We're at that point. It's time to push. It's time to push. Do you understand what I'm trying to tell y'all?

00:17:48.092 --> 00:17:53.057
It's time. He said, "You're looking there at that thread, that thin thread.

00:17:53.058 --> 00:17:59.277
Remember that hair-thin thread when I said Adam's lease is coming up?"Do you understand?

00:17:59.278 --> 00:18:05.260
We're about to step over the water's edge. We're about to step over the waterfall.

00:18:05.261 --> 00:18:11.007
And the Lord told me, He said, "You are about to see something I longed for you to see."Why?

00:18:11.008 --> 00:18:15.382
Because there was a lease. There was Adam's time frame of a 6,000-year window.

00:18:15.383 --> 00:18:23.395
And we're about to step into the 7,000-year window with the seven-year tribulation and all the things that we're about to see.

00:18:23.396 --> 00:18:33.500
We're about to see some radical things—radical, amazing things with the Holy Ghost and fire like we've never seen before. We've seen glimpses.

00:18:33.501 --> 00:19:02.319
The Lord said, "You people have seen glimpses with Azusa, with Brownsville, with the Welsh revival."He said, "You have seen glimpses that lasted just for a window.""But Brandon, what I'm about to do will pale in comparison to what is about to happen in these last days."And I'm so excited about it.

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:05.714
But then he said, "I have to give you a warning about the plague.

00:19:05.715 --> 00:19:14.576
I have to tell saints to stand and pray, and tell the people that I'm coming."And he talked about Psalm 91, and you all heard that.

00:19:14.577 --> 00:19:20.238
But then I saw an asteroid, and he was talking about this telescope called Lucifer, and then he called it Satan.

00:19:20.239 --> 00:19:33.045
And I thought, "This is a very demonic name."Of course, I'm not going to sit there and call it—I thought, "Am I hearing this right?"So Satan—this thing is called Devil—like, what is this?

00:19:33.046 --> 00:19:46.879
So I saw this telescope in the Arizona West, and it is a massive thing. I saw a lens on this thing that was ginormous.

00:19:46.880 --> 00:20:00.089
And as I was looking at this, I saw men talking in lab coats, like professors.

00:20:00.090 --> 00:20:12.639
I don't know how else to say this, but they were writing down, and they said, "The odds are in our favor. The odds are in our favor.

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:28.592
It's unlikely that this will happen."China was involved, and they were communicating back and forth at what they were seeing coming, and China said, "This is going to hit.

00:20:28.593 --> 00:20:33.536
This is serious."But the people in America were like, "I don't know.

00:20:33.537 --> 00:20:38.795
I don't think so."But China was taking it seriously. They were freaking out.

00:20:38.796 --> 00:20:53.119
I could see the Chinese men, who were very educated men, calculating and talking back and forth, and they knew something serious was about to happen and we were not going to avert it.

00:20:53.120 --> 00:21:00.763
As I was looking over into outer space, I saw a massive rock headed toward Earth.

00:21:00.764 --> 00:21:04.025
And they said, "We are not telling them because it will cause panic.

00:21:04.026 --> 00:21:12.256
We will not tell them for it will cause panic, but the odds are more in our favor that it will not happen.

00:21:12.257 --> 00:21:25.339
It will miss."But it will not. I saw another debris field, space debris, by this major rock. There was a whole bunch of them.

00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:39.294
This was not a small piece of rock; this was a massive piece of rock—planet-sized, like a massive-looking rock, huge.

00:21:39.295 --> 00:21:57.999
And the one that was beside it was smaller, but then the ones that they would consider "planet killers"were all behind it, like bunches of them.

00:21:58.000 --> 00:22:06.833
And as this thing was moving, all these others looked like a debris field behind it.

00:22:06.834 --> 00:22:14.959
I could see a debris field, and the Lord said, "Watch the sun.

00:22:14.960 --> 00:22:22.639
Watch your tides, for things are going to change and change quickly.

00:22:22.640 --> 00:22:35.279
Your water and your waves, the way the tides come in and come out because of the moon—things are going to start to shift like you've never seen before.

00:22:35.280 --> 00:22:44.111
And your tides are going to start to act very strange, like you've never seen before."Tides were higher than average.

00:22:44.112 --> 00:22:53.135
They came in further than what they were supposed to, and when they went out, they went out further than what they were supposed to.

00:22:53.136 --> 00:23:04.959
I heard this and I could see it. Something was affecting the tides—this rock, something serious.

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:14.479
The Lord said, "Watch the pressure on the earth, for a major volcano is about to erupt.

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:33.038
But not only will it be one volcano, but it will be multiple all at the same time."I saw earthquakes more than 9.0—huge earthquakes in more than just one place. They happened in multiple places at the same time.

00:23:33.039 --> 00:23:46.526
He said, "I told you and I warned you that it would affect the sun's light, the way it shines upon the earth, for it will cause the birds to want to migrate differently.

00:23:46.527 --> 00:23:53.963
It will cause the animals to breed differently because there is confusion in nature.

00:23:53.964 --> 00:24:06.893
They won't know when to fly south for the winter or go north for the summer."Things were acting weird. Animals and creation were acting weird.

00:24:06.894 --> 00:24:18.954
He said, "Even your agriculture, your flowering, and your planting, and things like that, will even be thrown off with what's coming."I saw the magnetic earth.

00:24:18.955 --> 00:24:28.464
I saw the pole and the way the earth was shifting and moving differently, and even your daytime will be different. The way the earth spins will be different.

00:24:28.465 --> 00:24:34.331
And most people say, "Well, it's a flat earth."I'm not going to argue about this; for what I saw, it's a round earth.

00:24:34.332 --> 00:24:43.512
And I'm telling you, even the sun will look different in the days ahead. You need to hear me because this is what I saw.

00:24:43.513 --> 00:24:58.706
The Lord said, "Look at Venice, Italy."And I could see the water in the city acting weird, and there was flooding, and there was a rise of the tides, and there were water events—that's what I'm going to call them.

00:24:58.707 --> 00:25:11.354
Water events are about to take place in Italy that have never happened before because of what's happening with our earth. Watch Venice, Italy. The Lord said, "Watch Rome.

00:25:11.355 --> 00:25:24.837
Watch the volcano that's about to go off even in Europe."This will be an event that is not just in the Ring of Fire, but this will be a global event that starts taking place.

00:25:24.838 --> 00:25:52.795
Then I saw India, and the Lord said, "Look at India, for a lot of the pagan temples will be destroyed with earthquakes in the days ahead."I saw the glory of God coming in, and there was a major revival all throughout India, all throughout all of these places where there were monkeys.

00:25:52.796 --> 00:26:04.040
I saw monkeys on temples, old shrines completely decimated by earthquakes. I'm talking broken down like the walls of Jericho.

